# Vercel serves only site/ (vercel.json outputDirectory). Keep the Python engine,
# tests, samples and — critically — /api off the deploy, so Vercel never mistakes
# /api for serverless functions or triggers a Python build. The engine runs on its
# own HF Space; Vercel hosts the static front-end only.
/api
/app
/src
/tests
/samples
/data
/docs
/.hf
/.hf-api
generate_samples.py
